{"tid":1641361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對狗屋問候狗嘅內容建議","createTime":"2019-10-09T10:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T14:34:55.000Z","uid":149829,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a10a15a9328de65545fe9449fe7947f6d1d94759","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"記唔記得點解我地當初由黑警變左鬧黑社會？<br />\n無錯，係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">心理學攻擊</span></strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n跟住落黎，我地要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">解離返集體落去個人攻擊</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你平時出面大嗌幾多次屌老母死黑驚都好，佢地作為一個集團，已經聽到慣曬，毫無感覺<br />\n所以以下落黎我建議大家要<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">針對個人</span></span></strong>，善用老豆搵仔，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>睇下狗隻有咩威水史大力表揚一下</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如今日新港城，可以問下馬鞍山DJ，<br />\n做咩<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">拋妻棄女娶整容保險雞</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢D咁光榮嘅事，就算最後佢地身邊嘅人扮無事唔出聲，都肯定會背後笑9佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n務求要做到當事人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">自我產生心理焦慮</span></ins></span>，從此破壞幸福生活圈<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家要努力搵多幾個痛點關心佢地呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拋磚引玉，開放討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"5f1b9bf5f827b8b506c23e7259a3b35743b1cfbe","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:17:50.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"10f1658bdb48fe679e9f041508c8c4e7a59cc679","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:20:19.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"45f942669a39e6eabb8a14eaf65bc856bb8460cc","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:22:08.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"5adee27b743a3eb045b60ed4b7e2507a6fa4f5c2","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"5f2727ca1d8f8567863b021281ca4275b58fe323","tid":1641361,"uid":84277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"攻心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1ff5a78f0ccd2a6dd15abfb96c6e1ef8c750f4","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:38:55.000Z","msg":"自推5/10"},{"pid":"052054857680e9b953f3096c374811dc660252e8","tid":1641361,"uid":190637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:40:29.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"d8788a12841e38c0847dbef2c5f9fddd923a51b3","tid":1641361,"uid":190637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"但冇樣冇no. 有老豆搵仔都冇用"},{"pid":"6ce42eefdd16945ea0fba13705072f3c809f7f2d","tid":1641361,"uid":149829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8788a12841e38c0847dbef2c5f9fddd923a51b3","tid":1641361,"uid":190637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl